title: Triathlon tips for your triathlon
tags:
- triathlon
---


0. Eat
Day before - high on curbs, less fiber, 

1. Swim
Calm the F**k down, slow your self down
Control your breathing

[3 Triathlon Swimming Technique Tips: Breathing for Freestyle](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lppZV1UIqwc)

2. Bike
Don't kill yourself on the bike. Make yourself aero, use aerobars

3. Run
Brik workouts. Train your body for transition from bike to run

[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vYUzG1yh4o8](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vYUzG1yh4o8)


